snippet.title: Wild West and Wizards - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy Now on Steam Early  Access! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1071290/Wild_West_and_Wizards/

Wild West and Wizards is an open world exploration game set in the Wild West with magic and rpg elements! Coming soon to Steam Early Access.

Website: http://wildwestandwizards.com
Twitter: http://twitter.com/lavabootsstudio
Discord: https://discord.gg/JMNt93p
